    title "VS Code extension"
    summary "Install the formal-ai extension into VS Code in one click. It downloads the latest signed .vsix and runs code --install-extension."
    install "Install in VS Code"
    installing "Installing…"
    installed "Installed into {cli}. Reload VS Code to start using it."
    noCli "No VS Code command-line tool was found. Install VS Code and enable the 'code' command in PATH."
